  "root_text": {
    "iti51:0.1": "Itivuttaka 51 ",
    "iti51:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti51:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti51:0.4": "Dhātusutta ",
    "iti51:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti51:2.1": "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, dhātuyo. ",
    "iti51:2.2": "Katamā tisso? ",
    "iti51:2.3": "Rūpadhātu, arūpadhātu, nirodhadhātu—",
    "iti51:2.4": "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso dhātuyo”ti. ",
    "iti51:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti51:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti51:3.1": "“Rūpadhātuṁ pariññāya, ",
    "iti51:3.2": "āruppesu asaṇṭhitā; ",
    "iti51:3.3": "Nirodhe ye vimuccanti, ",
    "iti51:3.4": "te janā maccuhāyino. ",
    "iti51:4.1": "Kāyena amataṁ dhātuṁ, ",
    "iti51:4.2": "phusayitvā nirūpadhiṁ; ",
    "iti51:4.3": "Upadhippaṭinissaggaṁ, ",
    "iti51:4.4": "sacchikatvā anāsavo; ",
    "iti51:4.5": "Deseti sammāsambuddho, ",
    "iti51:4.6": "asokaṁ virajaṁ padan”ti. ",
    "iti51:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti51:5.2": "Dutiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti51:0.1": "So It Was Said 51 ",
    "iti51:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti51:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti51:0.4": "Elements ",
    "iti51:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti51:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three elements. ",
    "iti51:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti51:2.3": "The elements of form, formlessness, and cessation. ",
    "iti51:2.4": "These are the three elements.” ",
    "iti51:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti51:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti51:3.1": "“Comprehending the element of form, ",
    "iti51:3.2": "not stuck in the formless, ",
    "iti51:3.3": "those who are released in cessation, ",
    "iti51:3.4": "they are conquerors of death. ",
    "iti51:4.1": "Having directly experienced <j>the element free of death, ",
    "iti51:4.2": "free of attachments; ",
    "iti51:4.3": "having realised relinquishment ",
    "iti51:4.4": "of attachments, the undefiled ",
    "iti51:4.5": "fully awakened Buddha teaches ",
    "iti51:4.6": "the sorrowless, stainless state.” ",
    "iti51:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti51:3.1": "Rūpadhātuṁ → rūpadhātu (sabbattha) ",
    "iti51:4.2": "phusayitvā → phassayitvā (bj, pts-vp-pli1); phussayitvā (sya-all) "
  },
